<inglise> ECSC High Authority: Decision No 24-54 of 6 May 1954 laying down in implementation of Article 66 (1) of the Treaty a regulation on what constitutes control of an undertaking </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA S&Ouml;E- JA TERASE&Uuml;HENDUS OTSUS nr 24-54 ettev&otilde;tja kontrollielemente k&auml;sitleva m&auml;&auml;ruse kohta asutamislepingu artikli 66 l&otilde;ike 1 rakendamisel 6. mai 1954 </eesti>
<inglise> THE HIGH AUTHORITY, </inglise>
<eesti> &Uuml;LEMAMET, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Article 66 of the Treaty; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse asutamislepingu artiklit 66 </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas by virtue of Article 66 (1) the High Authority must by regulation determine what constitutes control of an undertaking; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: artikli 66 l&otilde;ike 1 kohaselt tuleb ettev&otilde;tja kontrollielemendid m&auml;&auml;rata kindlaks &Uuml;lemameti m&auml;&auml;rusega; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas control may reside either in persons in whom certain rights are vested or in those who are entitled to exercise such rights with complete freedom; </inglise>
<eesti> kontrolli v&otilde;ivad omada isikud, kellele on antud teatavad &otilde;igused, v&otilde;i isikud, kellel on &otilde;igus selliseid &otilde;igusi t&auml;iesti vabalt kasutada; </eesti>
<inglise> After consulting the Council of Ministers; </inglise>
<eesti> p&auml;rast konsulteerimist ministrite n&otilde;ukoguga, </eesti>
<inglise> DECIDES: </inglise>
<eesti> OTSUSTAB: </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> The rights or contracts specified below shall constitute the elements of control of an undertaking, where either separately or jointly, and having regard to the considerations of fact or law involved, they make it possible to determine how an undertaking shall operate as regards production, prices, investments, supplies, sales and appropriation of profits: </inglise>
<eesti> J&auml;rgmised &otilde;igused v&otilde;i lepingud sisaldavad ettev&otilde;tja kontrollielemente, kui nad kas eraldi v&otilde;i &uuml;hiselt ning vastavaid asjaolusid v&otilde;i seadusi arvestades v&otilde;imaldavad m&auml;&auml;rata kindlaks ettev&otilde;tja tegevuse seoses tootmise, hindade, investeeringute, tarnete, m&uuml;&uuml;gi ning kasumieraldistega: </eesti>
<inglise> (1) Ownership or the right to use all or part of the assets of an undertaking; </inglise>
<eesti> 1) omandi&otilde;igus v&otilde;i &otilde;igus osaliselt v&otilde;i t&auml;ielikult kasutada ettev&otilde;tja vara; </eesti>
<inglise> (2) Rights or contracts which confer power to influence the composition, voting or decisions of the organs of an undertaking; </inglise>
<eesti> 2) &otilde;igused v&otilde;i lepingud, mis v&otilde;imaldavad m&otilde;jutada ettev&otilde;tja organite koosseisu, h&auml;&auml;letamist v&otilde;i otsuseid; </eesti>
<inglise> (3) Rights or contracts which enable any person, by himself or in association with others, to manage the business of an undertaking; </inglise>
<eesti> 3) &otilde;igused v&otilde;i lepingud, mis annavad mis tahes isikule v&otilde;imaluse kas &uuml;ksi v&otilde;i koos teistega juhtida ettev&otilde;tja &auml;ritegevust; </eesti>
<inglise> (4) Contracts made with an undertaking concerning the computation or appropriation of its profits; </inglise>
<eesti> 4) ettev&otilde;tjaga s&otilde;lmitud lepingud, mis k&auml;sitlevad ettev&otilde;tja kasumi arvutamist v&otilde;i eraldamist; </eesti>
<inglise> (5) Contracts made with an undertaking concerning the whole or an important part of its supplies or outlets, where the duration of these contracts or the quantities to which they relate exceed what is usual in commercial contracts dealing with those matters. </inglise>
<eesti> 5) ettev&otilde;tjaga s&otilde;lmitud lepingud, mis k&auml;sitlevad ettev&otilde;tja k&otilde;iki tarneid v&otilde;i turustusv&otilde;imalusi v&otilde;i olulist osa nendest, kui k&otilde;nealused lepingud on kestuse v&otilde;i koguste poolest ulatuslikumad k&otilde;nealuseid k&uuml;simusi k&auml;sitlevatest tavap&auml;rastest &auml;rilepingutest. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> There shall be no control of an undertaking within the meaning of Article 1 where, upon formation of an undertaking or increase of its capital, banks or financial institutions acquire shares in that undertaking with a view to selling them on the market but do not exercise voting rights in respect of those shares. </inglise>
<eesti> Kontroll ettev&otilde;tja &uuml;le artikli 1 t&auml;henduses puudub, kui pangad v&otilde;i finantsinstitutsioonid omandavad ettev&otilde;tja asutamise v&otilde;i kapitali suurendamisega seoses ettev&otilde;tja aktsiaid eesm&auml;rgiga viia need turule, kuid ei kasuta k&otilde;nealuste aktsiatega seotud h&auml;&auml;le&otilde;igusi. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The elements specified in Article 1 shall constitute control of an undertaking by individuals, undertakings or groups of persons or of undertakings who: </inglise>
<eesti> Artiklis 1 nimetatud elemendid on ettev&otilde;tte kontrollielemendid, kui &uuml;ksikisikud, ettev&otilde;tjad, isikute r&uuml;hmad v&otilde;i kontsernid: </eesti>
<inglise> (1) are holders of the rights or entitled to rights under the contracts concerned; </inglise>
<eesti> 1) on &otilde;iguste valdajad v&otilde;i kui neil on &otilde;igus k&otilde;nealustele &otilde;igustele asjaomaste lepingute alusel; </eesti>
<inglise> (2) while not being holders of such rights or entitled to rights under such contracts, have power to exercise the rights deriving therefrom; </inglise>
<eesti> 2) ei ole ise &otilde;iguste valdajad ega oma &otilde;igust k&otilde;nealustele &otilde;igustele nimetatud lepingute alusel, kuid omavad &otilde;igust kasutada nendest tulenevaid &otilde;igusi; </eesti>
<inglise> (3) in a fiduciary capacity own assets of an undertaking or shares in an undertaking, and have power to exercise the rights attaching thereto. </inglise>
<eesti> 3) omavad usalduskohustuse alusel ettev&otilde;tja vara v&otilde;i aktsiaid ning on p&auml;devad kasutama sellest tulenevaid &otilde;igusi. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> If, however, the power to exercise the rights of another person is derived from a legal act, the provisions contained in subparagraphs (2) and (3) of the preceding paragraph shall not apply where the holder of the power proves: </inglise>
<eesti> Kui &otilde;igus kasutada teise isiku &otilde;igusi p&otilde;hineb &otilde;igusaktil, siis ei kohaldata eelmise l&otilde;ike punkte 2 ja 3 juhul, kui &otilde;iguste valdaja t&otilde;endab, et: </eesti>
<inglise> (1) that his power may be revoked at any time; and </inglise>
<eesti> 1) k&otilde;nealuse &otilde;iguse saab igal ajal t&uuml;histada; </eesti>
<inglise> (2) that he is bound by special instructions from the donor; and </inglise>
<eesti> 2) ta on seotud &otilde;igusteandjalt saadud eri juhistega; </eesti>
<inglise> (3) that he is authorised to communicate to the High Authority, should it so request, the name and address of the donor. </inglise>
<eesti> 3) ta on kohustatud &Uuml;lemameti n&otilde;udmisel teatama talle &otilde;igusteandja nime ja aadressi. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 4 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 4 </eesti>
<inglise> This Decision shall enter into force within the Community on 1 June 1954. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev otsus j&otilde;ustub &uuml;henduses 1. juunil 1954. </eesti>
<inglise> This Decision was considered and adopted by the High Authority at its meeting on 6 May 1954. </inglise>
